    reading of favorite storybooks: A development study. Reading Research 
    Quarterly, 20, 458-481.

Sulzby, E.(1986).  Writing and Reading 
    :Signs of oral and written language organization in young children. In W.H. 
    Teale, & E. Sulzby(Eds.), Emergent literacy: Writing and reading.(pp.50-89). 
    Nowood,  N.J: Ablex.

Tharp, R.G.,& R.Gallimore.(1988). 
    Rousing minds to life. New York: Cambridge University Press.

Voss,M. M. (1996). Hidden literacies: 
    Children learning at home and at school. Portsmouth, NH: Heinemann.

